			<div class="comment-content"><p>Bill,<br />
That&#8217;s why I&#8217;ve come up with a great business idea: marijuana K-cups. We would sell an automatic joint roller and a line of MJ cartridges in various flavors and blends. Pop a cartridge into the machine and out pops a nicely rolled doobie. The perfect give for the stoner who has everything. For groups, buy our party-size cartridges for use in our hookah. Perhaps we could get Warren Buffett to invest. What do you think?</p>
</div>

