			<div class="comment-content"><p>You make a fabulous point. In fact, the UN is already leaning on Obama to send the feds into Colorado and Washington. See this blog: <a href="http://usahitman.com/untcwoml/" rel="nofollow">http://usahitman.com/untcwoml/</a></p>
<p>This news&#8211;the idea of the UN dictating our states&#8217; laws&#8211;should rally conservatives to the cause. Let&#8217;s stand up the UN and reassert our independence.  Maybe July 4, 2013, should a massive demonstration of our national and state sovereignty.  #LegalizeIt</p>
</div>

